                    <span>
                        DPD (UK)<br>
                    </span>
                </h5>
                <p>For postcodes in our <a class="link" href="/notifications/tg-collection-postcodes/">TG&nbsp;Courier collection zone</a> - London and North West England - our drivers will collect your parcel. Otherwise DPD&nbsp;will collect.</p>
                <p>Please refer to our documentation page for <a class="link" target="_blank" href="/information/documentation/">labelling instructions</a>.</p>
                <p>If you are not able to print any of your documents, please <a target="_blank" class="link" href="/contact-us/">get in touch</a> and we will be happy to post hard copies to you.</p>
                <p><strong>DPD&nbsp;Saturday, 10.30am and 12pm services</strong></p>
                <p>
                    Our DPD&nbsp;Saturday, 10.30am and 12pm services
                    <a class="link" href="#">
                        ship via our depot
                    </a>. You can drop off your consignment at
                    <a class="link" href="#">
                        one of our depots
                    </a>, book a collection from your door, or choose one of hundreds of DPD or UPS drop-off locations nationwide. Once your shipment has been delivered to our depot, we will process  it and forward your parcel to its final destination via DPD.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We'll collect and ship from our depot same day for
                    <a style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; " class="link" href="#">some collection postcodes</a>.  For all other postcodes, please add 1 extra working day for overnight  delivery to our depot.
                </p>
                <p>For Saturday delivery with DPD&nbsp;Saturday, your parcel must be collected on Friday for the above postcodes, and on Thursday for all others. Drop-offs at our depot must be made on Friday by 3pm. DPD may not hold parcels for Saturday delivery if they are collected earlier in the week.</p>
