                <p>For European deliveries, DPD offers the Predict service. If the recipient's mobile number is provided when booking through Megway Parcels, DPD will text them to announce a one-hour delivery window (e.g. 10am-11am). They will also receive an email.</p>
                <p>Not at home? You can change the delivery day, reroute the parcel to the nearest DPD Pickup shop, or arrange to have it left in a safe place or with a neighbour.</p>
